test httpd-client-0001 {Do an echo request} {

set reply [::httpd::test::send 10001 {POST /echo HTTP/1.0} {} {THIS IS MY CODE}]
::httpd::test::compare $reply {HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Content-Type: text/plain
Connection: close
Content-Length: 15

THIS IS MY CODE}
} {}

